TITLE: BackendMethod Decorator for Server-Side Method Execution
DESCRIPTION: Function decorator for defining server-side methods that can be called from the client. It includes type checking and options for controlling execution permissions and transaction handling.
SOURCE: https://github.com/remult/remult/blob/main/misc/public-api.md#2025-04-16_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
export declare function BackendMethod<type = unknown>(
  options: BackendMethodOptions<type>,
