TITLE: Defining EntityOptions Interface in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet defines the EntityOptions interface, which specifies configuration options for entities in Remult. It includes properties for setting entity caption, API access permissions, filters, ordering, and lifecycle hooks.
