TITLE: BackendMethodOptions Interface for Server Method Configuration
DESCRIPTION: Interface defining configuration options for backend methods, including access control, API routing, transaction handling, and queuing behavior. Provides detailed control over how backend methods execute.
SOURCE: https://github.com/remult/remult/blob/main/misc/public-api.md#2025-04-16_snippet_5

