TITLE: Displaying Task List in Sveltekit Component
DESCRIPTION: Svelte component that fetches tasks from the Remult repository and renders them as a list with checkboxes for the completed status.
SOURCE: https://github.com/remult/remult/blob/main/docs/tutorials/sveltekit/entities.md#2025-04-16_snippet_5

