TITLE: FindFirstOptionsBase Interface Definition
DESCRIPTION: Base interface for options specific to finding the first entity. It includes options for caching results and creating entities if not found.
SOURCE: https://github.com/remult/remult/blob/main/misc/public-api.md#2025-04-16_snippet_41

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
export interface FindFirstOptionsBase<entityType>
  extends LoadOptions<entityType> {
  /** determines if to cache the result, and return the results from cache.
   */
  useCache?: boolean
  /** If set to true and an item is not found, it's created and returned*/
  createIfNotFound?: boolean
}
```

