TITLE: Vite Configuration for Excluding Server-Only Packages
DESCRIPTION: Configuration for Vite bundler to exclude server-only packages from the frontend bundle, preventing compilation errors.
SOURCE: https://github.com/remult/remult/blob/main/docs/docs/using-server-only-packages.md#2025-04-16_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import { defineConfig } from 'vite'
import react from '@vitejs/plugin-react'

// https://vitejs.dev/config/
